{"tid":1586180,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"真左膠心聲：勇武們，你地做咩都支持！","createTime":"2019-09-21T22:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T00:07:32.000Z","uid":140326,"like":81,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"dacc11d70a2399feef188ebfc088d4b3c4c40af6","tid":1586180,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T22:13:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">起我底就知，我比好多熱狗 label 為左膠 泛民打手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一個左膠，見到風向撚不斷指責手足，我要比啲支持前線勇武。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77uvKLB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77uvKLB.jpg&h=7e95165b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地要100%信任前線決定<br />\n<br />\n外面指責，割蓆果啲，絕對唔係左膠，跟據電腦分析，<br />\n48%係3毛<br />\n47%係狗<br />\n唔係3毛就係狗<br />\n<br />\n個個都知果度有示威，正常唔係藍絲黑社會點會過去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64RNM0i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64RNM0i.png&h=62583555&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f59801d6c1ba5a22e2c9c8b351416f74b0928ef4","tid":1586180,"uid":140326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T22:14:46.000Z","msg":"前線無做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215ac590354ef8b9dc8e285732cf99908415865e","tid":1586180,"uid":140326,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T22:15:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">吳志森，燒山 呢啲死左膠唔該收皮</span>"},{"pid":"e3765a3c027613e06a52f221eea6782bd97dc789","tid":1586180,"uid":203619,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T22:16:00.000Z","msg":"真 咁多人唔打 打你？<br />\n冇前科我唔信啦<br />\n從來都係被動架啦"},{"pid":"e1e4a972a9cf846c8d5cdc6ab57bfacc39169e35","tid":1586180,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T22:16:35.000Z","msg":"公民自衛隊 以武制暴，絕對可靠"},{"pid":"ce8842a274b372015e0aac727b6d4d8bbfbd7736","tid":1586180,"uid":140326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,